# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../glossary.rst:23
msgid "Glossary"
msgstr "Glosarium"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../glossary.rst:25
msgid ""
"There is much technical terminology in today's fast-moving media-centric "
"world. If you find yourself wondering what a video production term or an "
"acronym means, you are certainly not alone. Like most industries, video "
"production has a language all its own. Here is a list of terms commonly "
"found in video editing. Becoming familiar with these terms only makes your "
"job easier."
msgstr ""
"Ada banyak terminologi teknis dalam dunia media yang bergerak cepat saat "
"ini. Jika Anda bertanya-tanya apa arti istilah produksi video atau akronim, "
"Anda tentu tidak sendirian. Seperti kebanyakan industri, produksi video "
"memiliki bahasanya sendiri. Berikut adalah daftar istilah yang umum "
"ditemukan dalam penyuntingan video. Mengenal istilah-istilah ini akan "
"mempermudah pekerjaan Anda."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../glossary.rst:34
msgid "Definitions"
msgstr "Definisi"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../glossary.rst:36
msgid ""
"These definitions are a work-in-progress. Please let us know if you need a "
"term defined by contacting support@openshot.org."
msgstr ""
"Definisi ini masih dalam proses pengerjaan. Silakan beri tahu kami jika Anda "
"membutuhkan definisi istilah dengan menghubungi support@openshot.org."

